#This readme shows how to run these programs.
#'>' means the start of the commandline in Unix system.

Excuting run.sh will automatically run all the programs in src,
including otsu method, mean method.

Original images store in directory ./pics/
Target imagess will be generated in directory ./pics/result/.

If you would like to run programs individually, follow the instruction below:
1.Otsu's method with median filter
>python ./src/median.py [original filename] [generated filename]
>python ./src/otsu.py [original filename] [generated filename]

2.mean method
>python ./src/mean.py [original filename] [generated filename] [threshold]
